Package: mdgm
Title: Mixture of Directed Graphical Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-06-10
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Authors@R: 
    person("Brandon", "Carter", , "brandon.carter@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bayesian inference for discrete spatial random fields using mixtures
    of directed graphical models (MDGM). Implements MCMC sampling over directed
    acyclic graph structures (spanning trees, acyclic orientations) with optional
    emission models for hierarchical observation processes. The C++ core provides
    efficient graph algorithms and sampling; the R interface exposes model
    construction, MCMC execution, and posterior summaries. Based on Carter and
    Calder (2024) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2406.15700>.
